column2: General: 1 Source of the original data: Federal Employment Agency. - 2 Territorial definition: Eastern Germany (as of September 1990 including West Berlin. - 3 Methodology: Up to and including December 2004 month-end figures, as of January 2005 mid-month figures. As of January 2004 unemployed persons excluding participants in aptitude testing and training measures. 4 Other: Early 2005: Rise influenced by inclusion of recipients of social assistance who are able to work.
